<B>__{moving view}
<A>__{clemenza moves along the booths that have been set up along the street: sausage cooking on an open fire; pork livers and sweetbeards. he stops for a sandwich, and makes an irritated gesture when the vendor expects to be paid. he crosses to a church sponsored booth with a great wheel of fortune, and slaps a dollar on a number. standing next to him is vito; they embrace.}
